v ZhETF (2000), vol. 71, 338-343Integrable SystemsJournal-ref: Pisma Zh.Eksp.Teor.Fiz. 71 (2000) 338-343; JETP Lett. 71 (2000)

235-238The recurrent relations between the eigenfunctions for $GL(N,\RR)$ and$GL(N-1,\RR)$ quantum Toda chains is derived. As a corollary, the Mellin-Barnesintegral representation for the eigenfunctions of a quantum open Toda chain isconstructed for the $N$-particle case.